text: "Dead End Street" is a 1966 song by British band The Kinks and was originally released as non-album single but has since included on the bonus tracks to their fourth studio album Face to Face. It went to number 5 in the United Kingdom and Germany, number 73 in the United States, number 62 in Australia, number 4 in Sweden, the Netherlands and New Zealand, number 7 in Ireland and Canada and number 6 in Norway. == References == Category:1966 songs Category:The Kinks songs Category:The Jam songs
